# XORAL — Supabase environment variables
# Copy to .env.local and fill in values from your Supabase project dashboard.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Setup:
# 1. Create a project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Run supabase/schema.sql in the SQL Editor
# 3. Disable email confirmation for dev (Authentication > Providers > Email) OR configure SMTP
# 4. Add these vars to Vercel project settings for production deploy
